                            <comment id="17933240" author="smiklosovic" created="Fri, 7 Mar 2025 09:05:42 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;So, this can be used but we just don&apos;t ship that configuration ootb? Shouldnt we bump to 1.5.x where it is removed?&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="17933296" author="brandon.williams" created="Fri, 7 Mar 2025 12:44:26 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;I&apos;m not sure what you are referring to, this CVE basically says if your logback config can be compromised, then code can be executed.  We don&apos;t ship logback in a configuration where anyone can write it.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="17933298" author="smiklosovic" created="Fri, 7 Mar 2025 12:49:31 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;ok, +1&#160;&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
